text:
Gajab nhi krte hein aap,daaru pi kr itna kaun sunata hai bewkoof. Thode matlabi toh aap bhi hein, khair mere saath ek acha photo daal dete toh maaf bhi kr dete. Ab yeah memoir nhi daale na toh sahi nhi krenge sahi bol rhe hein.
Apka best friend(bhale aap na maante ho)
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Chand Se Roshni Jyada
Aur Sitaron Se Kam Nikle,
Jab Bhi Main Tujhe Dekhun
Mera Hans-Hans Ke Dam Nikle.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Aasmaan Jitna Neela Hai,
SurajMukhi Jitna Peela Hai,
Paani Jitna Geela Hai,
Aapka Screw Utna Hi Dheela Hai.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Itna Khubsurat Kaise Muskura Lete Ho,
Itna Qatil Kaise Sharma Lete Ho,
Kitni Aasani Se Jaan Le Lete Ho,
Kisi Ne Sikhaya Hai...
Ya Bachpan Se Hi Kamine Ho?
author: Aditya  Mishra
